The paper proposes a novel deep learning architecture for estimating missing data in temporal data streams. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories. The paper also deals with medical data, which suggests that it could belong to the Signal and Image Processing (cs.SI) or Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) sub-categories.
